{"tid":1537670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如97比和理非發揮下？","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:22:11.000Z","uid":41704,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3380a8a32c17689bd14743378ee1985f50b9d1c5","tid":1537670,"uid":41704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:08:47.000Z","msg":"上次91勇武完都係pass唔到壓力測驗 不如今次真係試下拖個行李 唔著黑衫 唔叫口號 連口罩都唔帶？<br />\n<br />\n相信全世界媒體都會知我地做緊咩 就算佢地真係唔知 我地事後再係internet講返我地塞機場既目的<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做班狗唔敢亂咬人 如果亂咬既話 佢一咬錯遊客仲仆街<br />\n<br />\n不過咁樣做係真係需要人數夠多 同埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全部</span> 人都要有共識 有時自由發揮其實等於比位班UC入"},{"pid":"a239936a528b15676ebe4fbe49342d581680a569","tid":1537670,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:09:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57dbd31b3fed5c22013f1baba10274792417fef9","tid":1537670,"uid":38383,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"樓主仲停留係班狗唔會亂咬人既時期"},{"pid":"bce8ff984f5adcb497043c4f7984b15395326449","tid":1537670,"uid":153,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:12:18.000Z","msg":"收啦左膠"},{"pid":"ee8e8cce64d51daf8b469500c817864a18b127d6","tid":1537670,"uid":311193,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57dbd31b3fed5c22013f1baba10274792417fef9","tid":1537670,"uid":38383,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"樓主仲停留係班狗唔會亂咬人既時期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:13:00.000Z","msg":"真心 係佢哋接受唔到現實 仲以為和平係會贏"},{"pid":"1694b1e0dad3bd44eb6168f7ada92d7a66294647","tid":1537670,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57dbd31b3fed5c22013f1baba10274792417fef9","tid":1537670,"uid":38383,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"樓主仲停留係班狗唔會亂咬人既時期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"而家根本係一出嚟示威就拉咗先算<br />\nHong Kong=China"},{"pid":"720eacf758abe9444dc9efa21aa3e4f295b7365b","tid":1537670,"uid":92188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:13:23.000Z","msg":"要有啲和平集會，俾和理非出下，如果唔係，和理非會心灰盲目淡出"},{"pid":"cbb9f05a521520797f098ceb7d27ba97af21a96f","tid":1537670,"uid":131125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"57dbd31b3fed5c22013f1baba10274792417fef9","tid":1537670,"uid":38383,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"樓主仲停留係班狗唔會亂咬人既時期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:14:00.000Z","msg":"比較期待佢咬錯遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nanyway俾和理非發揮一日好啲<br />\n好似818咁，就算最後真係無咩用都無咩損失"},{"pid":"f19f991d1f16450268e488c56851